ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=71003b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"493f8f38a901c5427a413ca59ce4e43e13ed5696","tid":1746770,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"最多咪唔簽，等夠十日，自動生效。"},{"pid":"f2780596d6b6a7624088a6651fc67b2513f12bf6","tid":1746770,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"同流浮山刀手傳說一樣"},{"pid":"69447ba7c3e993cb8bd245a0b3eb1c3fc17956ea","tid":1746770,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"連侵都串鳩你老解得把死人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fec2e7b05e4d8bca6f27b3806a725d77cac61c0","tid":1746770,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5dd808cb5272b81167ca549f.jpg/OkcnpMzdu_lbZk_BEDBPs1YADpG0nt-OC51ccQudXHE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5dd808cb5272b81167ca549f.jpg%2FOkcnpMzdu_lbZk_BEDBPs1YADpG0nt-OC51ccQudXHE&h=61f7700a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50dc2e4cb24673b89ab7c51f89a911652e703584","tid":1746770,"uid":45727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"中共話 10 分鐘落到黎, 仲有4分鐘係咩? 要摺埋張被先? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e156d7cd86e0ce1ee26554c37d681df5de98d2","tid":1746770,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fec2e7b05e4d8bca6f27b3806a725d77cac61c0","tid":1746770,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5dd808cb5272b81167ca549f.jpg/OkcnpMzdu_lbZk_B